{"tid":1968790,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[PES2020]用香港隊打世界盃","createTime":"2020-04-12T03:04:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-13T05:29:36.000Z","uid":29010,"like":30,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"f11464f23f58b62671055257bd15d72d04cc4ddb","tid":1968790,"uid":29010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T03:04:12.000Z","msg":"放假好悶係屋企打個飛機先<br />\n<del>2018 FIFA世界盃</del>KONAMI盃 (因為個patch香港係經典隊所以開唔到世界盃)<br />\n分組就取代左亞洲最低排名嘅沙地<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3fPXMo1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3fPXMo1.jpg&h=73e027df&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n屌 數值真係差好遠<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/94f78Cn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F94f78Cn.jpg&h=089a5065&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n有無得唔握手?<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xLsqVho.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxLsqVho.jpg&h=9dbd8868&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n正選陣容 咁多場都係咁打啦 泊大巴<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HnKMEJ4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHnKMEJ4.jpg&h=bdced41d&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<del>俄羅斯 1-0 香港</del><br />\n俄羅斯 0-0 香港 (Save load)<br />\n黃威 1-0 烏龜<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/f4qHc35.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ff4qHc35.jpg&h=d544dcb2&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n我祖又入波又助攻 唔反了<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4vxZfhr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4vxZfhr.jpg&h=90b56fe2&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MHotS38.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMHotS38.jpg&h=43f92a28&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n暫時踢咁多場唯一一張牌<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mvWLaQP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmvWLaQP.jpg&h=ee1319e5&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n香港 2-0 埃及 但中國輝救左好多球 艾里奧都護左次空門<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ndn2XvQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fndn2XvQ.jpg&h=dd211cc9&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n呢個難度其實唔save load都可能出到線<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/g6FghvR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fg6FghvR.jpg&h=eb093808&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n16強贏1-0<br />\n<del>8強輸左場2-0再save load</del><br />\n孫銘絕殺2-1入4強<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CX48S4c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCX48S4c.jpg&h=c1f32e01&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n抽返烏拉圭好無feel<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kRcuCvT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkRcuCvT.jpg&h=086c39af&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n球員低數值好難入波 但泊大巴都有得打 晏啲打埋個兩場佢"},{"pid":"b7f4cf97f189dd8071bf211fc530ccc5cbeb0b0d","tid":1968790,"uid":34572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T03:05:41.000Z","msg":"維辛派蒲頭！"},{"pid":"ae56ceb875785f99c4997e8a64b75c071e8ff849","tid":1968790,"uid":35547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T03:14:16.000Z","msg":"點解唔拍片"},{"pid":"38a311514242742f9f140ced9851a04be2933260","tid":1968790,"uid":29010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ae56ceb875785f99c4997e8a64b75c071e8ff849","tid":1968790,"uid":35547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T03:14:16.000Z","msg":"點解唔拍片"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T03:16:12.000Z","msg":"要up上youtube? 同埋我打得好屎"},{"pid":"429308f5f735e23cddbdec51e9d629a1c6f88f51","tid":1968790,"uid":340081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T03:30:50.000Z","msg":"有神快拜 香港隊歷史性打入world cup final<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><